annen som utsatt."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "kultur"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "kultur|film"}, {"field": "category2", "value": "kultur|film|filmanmeldelser"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "3fbf0f1aadc5e615ea90ceea2421698f47bc3202adc9b550ec787646dc45a93f"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-04-30T10:32:29.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "FILM: Velskrudd dansk rystelse om heksejakt og overgrepsanklager, inspirert av Bjugn-saken. Mads Mikkelsen p\u00e5 sitt beste, som utsatt ansatt i barnehage."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article7035137.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Jaktenbild.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/ea398a676d05eb858099ea1cd8746986bc57f27e.jpg?59845b7d"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "F\u00f8rskolel\u00e6rer i helvete -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "ea398a676d05eb858099ea1cd8746986bc57f27e"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["trondheim kino", "kino", "dvd", "video", "kosmorama", "filmfestivaler"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "trondheim kino,kino,dvd,video,kosmorama,filmfestivaler"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["kultur", "filmanmeldelser", "film"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "arts-and-entertainment"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": "film"}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["den omsorgsfulle mannen", "festen", "jakten", "heksejakt"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["danmark", "bjugn", "cannes"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["thomas vinterberg", "mads mikkelsen", "arthur millers"]}, {"field": "kw-sentiment", "value": "negative"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["kultur/film/filmanmeldelser", "kultur", "kultur/film"]}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article7035137.ec